These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, white, brown, purple
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, gardening, baking, cooking
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, soy-milk, coffee
City: prague, colone, hamburg, london
House: colonial, townhouse, wooden, farmhouse
 1. the colonial house is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 2. the person drinking coffee is between the person who likes light-blue and the farmhouse house##2
 3. the person traveling to prague is the farmhouse house##1
 4. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 5. the colonial house is between the person who likes light-blue and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 6. the person traveling to london is on the right of the wooden house##1
 7. the townhouse house is the person who likes brown##1
 8. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Color           | brown | light-blue   | purple | white |
| Hobby   | filmmaking      | gardening | baking              | cooking |
| Beverage   | lemonade       | sprite     | coffee               | soy-milk    |
| City           | colone        | hamburg     | london           | prague       |
| House     | townhouse | wooden     | colonial                | farmhouse      |

