There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, mauve, yellow, red
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, gardening, singing, magic-tricks
 1. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 2. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person driving the taxi and the person who likes mauve##2
 4. the siglo-smoker is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 5. the person who likes yellow is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
10. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who likes red##1
11. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person driving the taxi##1
12. the person driving the jet-ski is the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Transport          | taxi       | trike      | jet-ski      | snowmobile      |
| City           | marseilles | hamburg | london | prague |
