 7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 8. the person who growsbegonia is the person watching disaster movies##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is the person driving the subway##1
10. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
