There are 4 different nationalities: polish, dutch, mexican, russian
House: townhouse, gothic-revival, wooden, cottage
4 different games are played: backgammon, chess, bridge, snooker
 1. the person playing bridge is the person who growsaconite##1
 2. the person playing chess is between the polish and the dutch##2
 3. the polish is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 4. the person who likes light-blue is the townhouse house##1
 5. the dutch is between the townhouse house and the person playing backgammon##2
 6. the cottage house is on the far left##1
 7. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the mexican##1
 8. the person who likes blood-red is the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person who likes azure is between the person playing chess and the mexican##2
10. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
11. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Color      | black     | azure | light-blue    | blood-red          |
