 8. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 9. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
10. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking water and the person who likes lavender##2
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
12. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
