The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, drama, martial-arts, spy
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, february, january, march
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the fan house##1
 6. the person watching spy movies is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the person watching fantasy movies is the owner of the goat##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person drinking cola##2
 9. the fan blues is on the far left##1
10. the fan house is between the person drinking cola and the fan r&b##2
11. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage          | cola       | lemonade       | juice | sprite    |
| Music-Genre         | blues     | house | r&b | funk     |
