The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, architect, dancer, chef
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, chestnut, light-blue, blood-red
 1. the dancer is the person playing monopoly##1
 2. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1
 3. the indian is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 4. the owner of the horse is the canadian##1
 5. the russian is on the left of the chinese##1
 6. the architect is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the person playing monopoly is between the owner of the frog and the indian##2
 8. the person playing whist is on the right of the dancer##1
 9. the person who likes white is the teacher##1
10. the person who likes white is between the person who likes blood-red and the person who likes light-blue##2
11. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
12. the person playing whist is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |      4      |
| Nationality      | indian   | canadian | russian       | chinese |
| Game         | bridge  | monopoly  | whist    | chess |
| Pet   | hedgehog   | horse | frog    | turtle       |
