 1. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's hobby is chestnuting##1
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the cape-cod house and the person who likes ebony##2
 3. the cottage house is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the fish##2
 4. the person who likes azure is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 5. the person who's hobby is writing is the person who growsmarigold##1
 6. the cottage house is the owner of the dog##1
 7. the person who likes grey is the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 9. the cottage house is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the wooden house is on the left of the person who's hobby is chestnuting##1
11. the person who's hobby is chestnuting is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who likes grey##2
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who likes azure and the owner of the dog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Pet      | fish      | dog         | mouse | ferret      |
| Flower           | marigold | sunflower | poppy | balloon-flower     |
| House   | wooden         | cottage          | victorian  | cape-cod |
| Hobby         | writing        | chestnuting  | traveling | drawing   |
| Color     | chestnut    | ebony         | grey     | azure     |

