.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-18::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, designer, journalist, fisherman
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, board-games, camping, photography
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, poppy, amaryllis, iris
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, havana, dunhill, alhambra
House: tower, modern, art-deco, cottage
 1. the person who growsiris is between the dunhill-smoker and the modern house##2
 2. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 3. the havana-smoker is the art-deco house##1
 4. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
 5. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 6. the havana-smoker is on the right of the designer##1
 7. the project-manager is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the fisherman is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
10. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the tower house##1
11. the fisherman is between the person who's hobby is photography and the tiparillo-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |   4    |
| Job          | project-manager  | fisherman  | designer  | journalist   |
| Hobby   | photography     | writing | camping     | board-games |
| Flower           | amaryllis   | iris     | poppy      | daisy   |
| Cigar         | dunhill   | alhambra    | tiparillo  | havana |
| House     | tower | cottage     | modern | art-deco |

