.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, august, april, december
House: tower, farmhouse, colonial, palace
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, dannemann, montecristo, tiparillo
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, balloon-flower, daffodil, dahlia
City: hamburg, london, venice, boston
 1. the montecristo-smoker is the farmhouse house##1
 2. the tower house is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who growsdahlia and the tiparillo-smoker##2
 4. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who growspoppy##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person traveling to boston##2
 6. the person traveling to london is on the right of the palace house##1
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1
 8. the tower house is the person traveling to venice##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |       4       |
| Birthday      | december    | august     | february        | april          |
| House         | palace | farmhouse   | tower        | colonial |
| Cigar           | old-henry   | montecristo | tiparillo | dannemann      |
| Flower   | dahlia    | balloon-flower      | poppy          | daffodil        |
| City     | hamburg  | london   | venice      | boston           |

