.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, oliveros, davidoff, bolivar
City: miami, prague, paris, edinburgh
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, juice
There 4 different types of food: plum, potato, pumpkin, grapefruit
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, august, december, january
 1. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person drinking juice and the person eating plum##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person eating potato and the person who's birthday is in december##2
 4. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 5. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person eating potato##1
 6. the person eating potato is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 7. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 8. the person traveling to paris is the person eating pumpkin##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
10. the havana-smoker is the person drinking cola##1
11. the person drinking cola is the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Cigar         | davidoff  | oliveros | bolivar | havana |
| City   | edinburgh      | prague   | paris      | miami    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate | juice        | cola     |
| Food         | plum  | potato  | pumpkin     | grapefruit      |
| Birthday     | june | january      | august   | december       |

 